      <title>法国通胀在选举前两天恢复放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/french-inflation-resumes-slowdown-two-days-before-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国通胀略有放缓 — — 这强化了欧洲央行开始削减历史高利率的决定，并为总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙在选举前两天带来了经济亮点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/french-inflation-resumes-slowdown-two-days-before-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 06:45:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国消费者支出和服务增长超出预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/uk-economy-grew-faster-than-expected-as-consumers-spent-more</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国经济走出衰退，出现两年多来最强劲的增长势头，且增速超过之前的预期，服务业和消费者支出双双推动经济上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/uk-economy-grew-faster-than-expected-as-consumers-spent-more</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 06:06:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
